	题图来自&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?sa=i&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=images&amp;cd=&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=0CAYQjB0&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orartswatch.org%2Fartswatch-looks-ahead-to-the-next-portland-international-film-festival%2F&amp;ei=DhCCVcPkG4m1ogSD74DAAg&amp;bvm=bv.96041959,bs.1,d.cGU&amp;psig=AFQjCNF9qeGxS24VegxNjuxqj7RClWbtAg&amp;ust=1434673342648095">www.orartswatch.org</a> 
</p>
		</div>
